The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or recent scholarly debates on the topic. The historical accounts are subject to interpretation, and the complexity of the spread of Islam involves numerous socio-political factors that may not be fully captured in this report. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources may limit the depth of analysis regarding primary historical events and narratives.